(44, 13, 6, 26, 13, 10, 16, 'false prophet', 'False Prophets and Deception', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of false prophets misleading people. In Acts, Bar-jesus is identified as a false prophet, while Ezekiel condemns prophets who claim peace when there is none. This connection highlights the consequences of such deception.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
